text: The Frogmen is a 1951 American World War II action movie directed by Lloyd Bacon and starring Richard Widmark, Dana Andrews, Gary Merrill, Jeffrey Hunter, Robert Wagner, Warren Stevens. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * Category:1951 war movies Category:1951 action movies Category:American action movies Category:World War II movies Category:Movies directed by Lloyd Bacon
